e their life.</span><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\"><strong>The question is: What are you going to do with it?</strong></span><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">Right now, Waggier is offering <strong>35% off the CalmBowl</strong> for dog parents who want to take action before it's too late.</span><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">But here's the catch: Because of the premium 304 stainless steel and specialized rotating blade barrier system, they can only produce limited quantities each month.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggk6fEZeoPc_text","label":"ggk6fEZeoPc_text","default":"<p><a href=\"https://waggier.com/products/waggier-calmbowl\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#324FE8;font-size:16px;\"><strong><u>Click the button below now to check if Waggier CalmBowl is still available with the special discount!</u></strong></span></a></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8uKrvdrn__text","label":"gg8uKrvdrn__text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong>Covered by a 90-Day Money Back Guarantee</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWU0mwVWh3_text","label":"ggWU0mwVWh3_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">If the CalmBowl doesn't completely transform your dog's eating, Waggier will refund every penny.</span><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">They're that confident because they know: once you see your dog eating calmly instead of gulping desperately, you'll never go back to regular bowls.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggy3RbjeAca_text","label":"ggy3RbjeAca_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:22px;\"><strong>You Have Two Choices</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKXKZJgesf_text","label":"ggKXKZJgesf_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#00000